<ol>
  <li>Sales of shares to raise new capitals are said to occur in primary market</li>
  <li>In stock markets where people buy and sell existing shares, stock exchange are really markets for
secondhand shares, but they prefer to describe themselves as secondary market, which sounds more
important.</li>
</ol>

